  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/218ac1c2db1e13462505ec8f4d6c1eba.avif?t=1646804397\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/43f16906c8a3367d739353eb6e0fe322.poster.avif?t=1646804397\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/43f16906c8a3367d739353eb6e0fe322.webm?t=1646804397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/43f16906c8a3367d739353eb6e0fe322.mp4?t=1646804397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A puzzle game with matchsticks where your mind will be constantly challenged after each level.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Move, add or remove sticks to obtain the correct answer before you run out of moves.<br></li><li> One puzzle may contain more than one solution.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/d3c0f4aaf86be9bb6f5674397ac5b556.avif?t=1646804397\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/b3767fb72215e1e034c66f79232b6012.poster.avif?t=1646804397\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/b3767fb72215e1e034c66f79232b6012.webm?t=1646804397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/b3767fb72215e1e034c66f79232b6012.mp4?t=1646804397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No time, no score, no pressure! Take your time at each level.<br></li><li> 60 carefully selected puzzles.<br></li><li> Practice your memory, logical and spatial thinking.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/0cc1251a335ba839ec28d06914aef3c8.avif?t=1646804397\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/4545913855698651d14818b79cb4a151.poster.avif?t=1646804397\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/4545913855698651d14818b79cb4a151.webm?t=1646804397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614340/extras/4545913855698651d14818b79cb4a151.mp4?t=1646804397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 3 beautiful and original themes to be selected<br></li><li> Original soundtrack exclusive to this game, by Tatyana Jacques<br></li><li> Coding and development by the programmer Alexander Froelich </li></ul>",
